      • scheduleLogRolloverEnforcer

        public void scheduleLogRolloverEnforcer()
        We schedule a process to run every minute, that, when it detects that an hour is rolled over (the minute of hour is 0), writes an entry into every log with mostly NULLs. This will force the roll over process to work.
        See Also:
        Remko Popma's comment on Stackoverflow
